	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="http://www.cc65.org/" class="postlink">Assembler - CA65</a> (part of CC65 C compiler)
<br /><a href="http://nintendoage.com/forum/messageview.cfm?catid=22&amp;threadid=7155" class="postlink">Tutorial for a starter</a>
<br />
<br />I don't use Unix, but as far as I know, things aren't good about NES development there regarding tools for graphics and sound, so you probably would need something like Wine to run Windows tools.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


